OL,3,CNewhaven murder: Killer took victims'
OL,4,Cchildren to Mcdonald's after attack
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a married couple in Newhaven
OL,8,Fin East Sussex.
OL,10,FDerek Martin admitted the manslaughter
OL,11,Fof Chloe and Joshua Bashford in 2023 -
OL,12,Fbut denied murdering them, claiming he
OL,13,Fhad a history of mental health
OL,14,Fproblems.
OL,16,FToday (Friday 24 October) a jury found
OL,17,FMartin guilty of murder.
