OL,3,CNewhaven murder: Killer took victims'
OL,4,Cchildren to Mcdonald's after attack
OL,6,FFollowing the murders, Martin
OL,7,Fcollected the couple's four children
OL,8,Ffrom school, and took them to
OL,9,FMcDonalds, before dropping them off
OL,10,Fand heading to a police station.
OL,12,FBelow is a timeline of the events and
OL,13,Fmovements of Martin during and after
OL,14,Fthe murders of Chloe and Joshua
OL,15,FBashford.
OL,17,FJune 9 2023: Day of the killing
