OL,3,CNewhaven murder: Killer took victims'
OL,4,Cchildren to Mcdonald's after attack
OL,6,FAt 11:57am on the 9 June 2023, police
OL,7,Fbelieve 67-year old Derek Martin
OL,8,Fentered the Bashford's home in Lewes
OL,9,FRoad, Newhaven.
OL,11,FIt's not clear exactly when - but
OL,12,FChloe Bashford was struck with a
OL,13,Fhammer and stabbed.
OL,15,F12:20pm: Martin carries out second
OL,16,Fmurder
OL,18,FLess than half an hour later, at
OL,19,Faround 12:20pm, Joshua Bashford
OL,20,Freturned home from work in his van for
OL,21,Fthe final time.
