OL,6,FHe was greeted in the hallway of his
OL,7,Fhome by Derek Martin brandishing a
OL,8,Fknife.
OL,10,FJoshua ran upstairs to get away, but -
OL,11,Flike his wife - was stabbed too,
OL,12,Fbefore being strangled by Martin.
OL,14,F1:30pm: Martin's coverup
OL,16,FA meter reader knocks at the door an
OL,17,Fhour later- but there's no sign of
OL,18,Flife at the house, and he leaves.
