OL,6,FAt 2:20pm Martin appears on the
OL,7,Fdoorbell camera - topless wearing
OL,8,Fshorts - having changed his clothes
OL,10,FHe's then captured putting his hand
OL,11,Fover the lens -and removing the device.
OL,13,FAfter 3pm: A trip to McDonald's
OL,15,FMarten carried on as normal that
OL,16,Fafternoon as if nothing had happened.
OL,18,FHe's recorded on CCTV in the Costa
OL,19,Fcoffee shop in Peacehaven, where he
OL,20,Fbought an afternoon treat for the
OL,21,FBashford's four children.
