OL,6,FHe then headed to their school where
OL,7,Fhe collected them.
OL,9,FMartin spent half an hour with the
OL,10,Fchildren at McDonald's in Newhaven,
OL,11,Fbefore driving to Brighton to drop
OL,12,Fthem off with their grandmother - his
OL,13,Fex-wife.
OL,15,F5:20pm: Martin alerts police to the
OL,16,Fmurders
OL,18,FMartin went into a Co-Op store and
OL,19,Fbought larger which he drank on the
OL,20,Fbeach, before heading to the police
OL,21,Fstation.
