OL,3,CNewhaven murder: Killer took victims'
OL,4,Cchildren to Mcdonald's after attack
OL,6,FOnce there, Martin walked into the
OL,7,Fstation and said "I've killed two
OL,8,Fpeople".
OL,10,FAsked if he suffered with any mental
OL,11,Fhealth problems, Martin replied "a
OL,12,Fbit" before saying he suffers with
OL,13,Fanxiety and depression.
OL,15,F24 October 2025: Guilty
OL,17,FOn 3 August 2023 Martin admitted the
OL,18,Fmanslaughter of Joshua and Chloe, but
OL,19,Fpleaded not guilty to murder.
